tweet: My final annual salary (gross) circa 2013 was about 32k. I worked 12-16 hour days, 5-10 at weekends. It‚Äôs not a career any more. It‚Äôs just a constant grind with a gov that say you can‚Äôt be trusted in your judgement anyway.

name: Hannah (RP)
description: NHS Data Tamer. Artist. Pokemon addict. She/Her. David Tennant lover. Advocate. Ambassador for #AutisticaPlay #ActuallyAutistic
tweet: Teachers are vilified as they are perceived to have an easy 9-3 babysitters job with long breaks and stacks of time. In reality, we feed poor kids, make statements in court about child abuse, neglect our own medical needs and because we believe in what we do/did.

name: Hannah (RP)
description: NHS Data Tamer. Artist. Pokemon addict. She/Her. David Tennant lover. Advocate. Ambassador for #AutisticaPlay #ActuallyAutistic
tweet:
